    "By embracing this dynamic construct, we can better understand and navigate the complexities of integrating generative AI into scientific authorship, ultimately advancing the pursuit of knowledge in the digital age.",
    "Why is it important to address this issue in this theoretical matter?",
    "There are several recent examples where authors have published materials in leading journals that have been retracted.",
    "Specifically, an article in Frontiers in Cell and Developmental Biology was retracted because the authors included inaccurate AI-generated figures (Guo et al. 2024; Frontiers Editorial Office 2024; Kim et al. 2024).",
